In a whirl of flames, blue, black and red. . .  the trio of terror appeared in the hall of Olympus.<br>
Alecto, Megaera and Tisiphone all grinned as they looked about with wild eyes at the Gods.<br>
<br>
Instantly they found their Mother Gaia and bowed in great respect of the Goddess. Alecto then spoke.<br>
&quot;Mother, your pressence brings honor to my eyes.&quot; She grinned.<br>
<br>
Megaera listened to Tisiphone's whispered words.<br>
&quot;We feel the same Mother.&quot;<br>
